## Remarks  
方法释放与关联的<xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream>非托管资源和托管资源。 `Close` 如果拥有基础<xref:System.Net.Sockets.Socket>, 则也会将其关闭。 <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream>

如果与关联`Close` , 则该方法将关闭 TCP 连接, 但不会释放关联<xref:System.Net.Sockets.TcpClient>的。 <xref:System.Net.Sockets.TcpClient> <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream>

## Examples  
下面的代码示例关闭<xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream>。

```vb
' Example for closing the NetworkStream.
' Close the NetworkStream
myNetworkStream.Close()
```

```csharp
// Example for closing the NetworkStream.

// Close the NetworkStream
myNetworkStream.Close();
```

```cpp
// Example for closing the NetworkStream.
// Close the NetworkStream
myNetworkStream->Close();
```
